snippet.title: The First Turnabout Redux - FULL PLAYTHROUGH
snippet.description:
​A fan game re-creation of the first Ace Attorney case...

...but (slightly) more realistic.

For example, it uses real trial procedures such as direct examination and impeachment! (from the official site)
Download: https://besheh.itch.io/ace-attorney-the-first-turnabout-redux
